Then there need to be fewer knockups. They interrupt channels, and are essentially a stun, which allows other champions to easily hit their (more powerful because they are affected by tenacity) CC, and chain them together until a target is dead, without them being able to do anything at all, even flash or Zhonya's. At the very least, airborne champions should be able to flash or use other mobility spells.

